{"tid":1953681,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[5分鐘狗車即到] 曱甴舖門口排曬隊，坐到好逼，快啲黎封左間曱甴舖","createTime":"2020-04-01T10:06:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T04:47:18.000Z","uid":52090,"like":65,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"11c55ad7bc996984ccb859c920c903605b1866a4","tid":1953681,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:06:50.000Z","msg":"電郵，App，電字表格，短訊只有限度服務<br />\n<strong>請直接Call</strong> 28680000 ，999 ，1823<br />\n各區狗屋熱線：<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/contact_us.html#hotlines\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Fppp_tc%2Fcontact_us.html%23hotlines&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnX8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=60674689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/contact_us.html#hotlines</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>你班人都唔識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我打咗兩三次去舉報 好快有人嚟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">盡量唔好講舖頭名 淨係話乜乜街幾多號<br />\n我見到 嗰d曱甴舖 ， 門口排曬隊 又任人入唔使探熱 坐到逼一滴，麻煩你哋搵人睇一睇<br />\n捉曬呢啲曱甴就啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n打咗五分鐘到就有架EU衝過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n#185 藍店違反防疫條例 任坐任入 打熱線舉報被cut線 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1953319/page/8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1953319/page/8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">深藍曱甴舖，早日執笠破產</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n香港獨立，唯一出路<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n不分化，不割蓆<br />\n黑警死全家</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"2e7e997208902d36317d53c88ab857b693c630a1","tid":1953681,"uid":52090,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vVnte4Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvVnte4Y.png&h=120384f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4ab62410d1795eb896b8762ebd147255b0c372b","tid":1953681,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:08:48.000Z","msg":"推比更多人睇"},{"pid":"f0ac09785c1378492a29f6565079d0c21518beaf","tid":1953681,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c2aed05f016f0e12df86b8442891dc7ee62ef9","tid":1953681,"uid":134087,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:09:00.000Z","msg":"樓主自細講開大話<br />\n世界仔嚟 抵讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e78e461b9ab564019c8c62c6405baf8536be0273","tid":1953681,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:09:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86f4eebbf8be3ae688f8f6b81d8585574bbacc60","tid":1953681,"uid":52090,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"98c2aed05f016f0e12df86b8442891dc7ee62ef9","tid":1953681,"uid":134087,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:09:00.000Z","msg":"樓主自細講開大話<br />\n世界仔嚟 抵讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:09:38.000Z","msg":"唔係我，係link入面個巴打"},{"pid":"d9343f23ec5c2a44903b89b9f02d11f1234d6442","tid":1953681,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:10:06.000Z","msg":"直接打999"},{"pid":"99af11a52eb8ec75e00f3e53ffd618e0c97c0a95","tid":1953681,"uid":52090,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T10:10:27.000Z","msg":"【倒數4月2號】功能組別轉組集中帖！叫齊人登記左未！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1949718/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1949718/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"eaf416a3d93cc4d1bd5db19c184e0ce952b448a7","tid":1953681,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":